{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"ac8f64134b","title":"反对农业合作化反对统购统销","origin":"《高等学校右派言论选编》（中共中国人民大学委员会，1958年8月）。","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"b71a42f43e","index":0,"year":1957,"month":6,"day":null,"articleId":"ac8f64134b"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"e759231f2d","name":"农业战线","type":"主题/事件"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-fanyou","name":"中国反右运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"2499a730cb","name":"云南大学"},{"id":"2feb30ed81","name":"李佳培"},{"id":"4bace9cfe2","name":"朱祥亭"},{"id":"684bf724d3","name":"章忠实"},{"id":"a801366d30","name":"谭东北"},{"id":"bc8ab6b645","name":"张士林"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-fanyou":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"19ff8d4633","type":"title","text":"反对农业合作化反对统购统销","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ac8f64134b"},{"id":"59c06d4313","type":"authors","text":"云南大学李佳培章忠实朱祥亭谭东北张士林","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ac8f64134b"},{"id":"b9eae5d48f","type":"paragraph","text":"“几年来党的政策是和马列主义有很大的出入的。如农业合作化时强调农民自私落后，与马列主义认为劳动群众是历史的创造者的理论根本不符。”（云南大学  李佳培）","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ac8f64134b"},{"id":"b997393389","type":"paragraph","text":"“合作化表面上强调自愿，实际上造成压力，不入社就是落后，入了社要退社就困难万分。”（云南大学　章忠实）","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ac8f64134b"},{"id":"90a8012f52","type":"paragraph","text":"“合作社有了强迫现象，有些合作社有问题，干部一团糟。四川合作社有减产现象，农民并不是自愿入社。”（云南大学　朱祥亭）","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ac8f64134b"},{"id":"931cc4b109","type":"paragraph","text":"“农业合作化后猪肉少了，至少农业合作化问题，政府把粮食收光了。”（云南大学　钱××）","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ac8f64134b"},{"id":"f618afd4f6","type":"paragraph","text":"“统购统销的成绩和缺点差不多，即使有成绩，也是从农民那里榨来的。”（云南大学  谭东北）","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ac8f64134b"},{"id":"abf58818e0","type":"paragraph","text":"“甚么合作化，农民还不是破破烂烂？！农村现在乱七八糟，农民生活没有提高。”（云南大学  张士林）","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ac8f64134b"}],"page":{"id":"37f48775f8","publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ac8f64134b","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}